items.name: Griffith Mesh Task Chair
items.description: The Griffith Mesh Task Chair combines a modern, breathable mesh design with adjustable features for comfort throughout your workday. Features include adjustable armrests, tilt tension, and seat height, giving you control over your seating experience. Suitable for any office or home space.

items.name: Griffith Mesh Task Chair
items.description: The Griffith Mesh Task Chair offers a perfect blend of style and functionality for your office space. The breathable mesh back allows for air circulation to keep you cool, while the padded seat ensures comfort during long work sessions. Customize your seating experience with easy-to-adjust seat height and tilt lock features.

items.name: Griffith Mesh Task Chair Deluxe
items.description: The Griffith Mesh Task Chair Deluxe edition takes comfort to the next level with additional lumbar support and a headrest. The mesh back design promotes air flow, and the chair includes multiple adjustment settings to tailor the fit perfectly to your body. An ideal investment for anyone who spends a lot of time working at a desk.
